            <description><![CDATA[秋冬嘴唇容器起皮干燥的宝一定要备上，某宝一支可是要39.9的，现在9.9拿下！通透莹润得啫喱质地，上嘴很滋润白天薄薄涂一层可以当作口红打底保湿，晚上厚敷作为唇膜，第二天起来嘴唇都嫩嘟嘟的，小小一个放包包里也方便~ <br> <br>【9.9】日本叮叮润唇膏 <img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uap6t9xj20j60j4dgs.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uapy9h1j20j60j7wfx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uaqqzndj20j60j6myw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uarkganj20j60j6t9i.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uasco5lj20j60j60t3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h64uat4hjtj20h80g6t8z.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
